  "context": "10 Supervisor, campus budget officer, and approved by the Campus Director/University President prior to the rendition of overtime services.\n\nSection 8 The immediate supervisor, as accountable officer, shall ascertain the number of hours rendered as indicated in the Daily Time Record (DTR) commensurate to the output(s) presented. Proof(s) shall no longer be attached to the DTR, and the immediate supervisor may require additional supporting documents and other objective evidences.\n\nTable VI.3 Seasonal/Occasional Designation\n\n| Designations | Maximum Allowable No. of Hours for Overtime (in a week) | Maximum Allowable No. of Hours for Over-time (in a semester – 18 weeks) |\n|---|---|---|\n| University Director (So- cio-cultural Affairs, PESA, REC, EALRG, Alumni Affairs, FLS, IMD, GAD, Sentro ng Wika at Kultura | 9 | 162 |\n| University Director. Admission & Testing (except 2nd semester of the academic year) | 6 | 108 |\n| Unit Head, Admission & Testing (except 2nd semester of the academic year) | 6 | 108 |\n| Unit Head, IMD | 6 | 108 |\n| Unit Head, FLS | 6 | 108 |\n| Unit Head, GAD | 6 | 108 |\n| Unit Head, REC | 6 | 108 |\n| Unit Head, ITSO | 6 | 108 |",
